Uses of Package
com.serena.dmclient.api

Packages that use com.serena.dmclient.api
com.serena.dmclient.api This package provides classes and interfaces for querying, updating, creating, and deleting Dimensions CM objects such as item revisions and requests. 
com.serena.dmclient.collections This package provides the collection interfaces that represent groups of Dimensions objects. 
com.serena.dmclient.objects This package provides the interfaces and classes for constructing and accessing Dimensions administration objects.
